From {{etyl|fr|en}} {{m|fr|automatique}}, from {{etyl|grc|en}} {{m|grc|αὐτόματον}}, neuter of {{m|grc|αὐτόματος||self-moving, moving of oneself, self-acting, spontaneous}}, from {{m|grc|αὐτός||self, myself}} + {{m|grc|μέμαα||to wish eagerly, strive, yearn, desire}}.

